N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 138.1 - General

State Regulations

This Part prescribes rules and regulations
governing administration of the Justice Court Assistance Program. This program
was established by the Legislature to provide a means by which towns and
villages may obtain limited State funding to improve operation of their Justice

Courts. Notes
